1. Which of the following is the best way to describe futurecasting?
Solution : C. Fishing for future opportunities that will give us a compentitive advantage

2. Why should you futurecast before you start ideating?
Solution : B. To future-proof your innovation work

3. Which of the following is a good example of an activity that helps you futurecast?
Solution : A. Collect the latest weird and wacky cultural experiences in your city

4. How will your futurecast impact your innovation process?
Solution : C. It will stretch your team to create a bolder and more relevant "How Might We" Quest to drive innovation
